Throughout the semester, we constantly discussed what kind of school cirriculum that should be implemented in the public school system. <a href="http://www.acenet.edu/the-presidency/columns-and-features/Pages/Teaching-Us-to-Think-The-Role-of-the-Liberal-Arts.aspx"> An article </a> I read recently brought an interesting point to show how much better the liberal arts cirriculum would be for K-12. 